<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA88">
<l>atunaṉ ṟitutīteṉ ṟaiyap paṭātē</l>
<l>matuniṉṟa taṇṭuḻāy mārvaṉ – potuniṉṟa</l>
<l>poṉṉaṅ kaḻalē toḻumiṉ muḻuviṉaikaḷ</l>
<l>muṉṉaṅ kaḻalu muṭintu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without being in doubt that that is good [and] this is evil,</l>
<l>worship the [feet with] golden anklets that rest common [to all],</l>
<l>[the feet] of him with honey-rich cool tulsi on his chest.</l>
<l>All former deeds will end [and] dissolve.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
